    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a nice luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors; the leather seats show some light creasing but no tears, and all electronic features are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes. It drives straight and quiet, making it a reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it.",
