      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and reliable performance. This automobile offers a refined driving experience, featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust mechanical profile. It stands as a testament to quality upkeep, ready to provide its next owner with dependable service and a sophisticated road presence.",
      "price": 33500.0,
