      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains crisp, with the double VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure precise cam timing across the power band. Torque is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. To address platform-specific weak points, the rear subframe has been reinforced, maintaining structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the car's celebrated handling geometry. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with use, the mechanical vitals are sorted for immediate performance.",
